    "updated_at": "2015-11-29T17:56:36Z",
    "body": "- Does it reproduce if you set `resizable` to true?\n- Does it work better if you check the current size and resize only if it's different than the current size?\n- Are you getting many move events (I imagine it's constantly firing while you move the window)? If that's the case, consider using a timer to delay the resize (e.g. once every 100ms) which might provide a smoother experience.\n"
