    "created_at": "2015-12-03T08:32:31Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-12-03T08:32:31Z",
    "body": "It seems to me that resizing a window while it is being moved/dragged is the issue here. I haven't really tested resizing when the window isn't being dragged but I'm almost sure it will work. \n\nRe @etiktin\nI'm not sure I quite understand what you are staying but the issue occurs on all screens. Calling setSize only when the current window size is different to the target window size doesn't work because most of the time getSize reports the old window size, as the window keeps snapping back to its old size. \n"
  },
