    "updated_at": "2016-07-09T13:08:28Z",
    "body": "The same behavior can be reproduce in Chrome apps, since Electron is using Chromium's code for creating windows, we are not able to fix this on Electron's side. I suggest making a reproducible example as Chrome app, and reporting it to Chromium' issues list instead.\n\nI'm closing this as won't fix.\n"
